# NexusViewPro 🚀

**NexusViewPro** is a lightweight Python library designed for Data Scientists and Jupyter Notebook users.
It allows you to seamlessly render live websites and embed YouTube videos directly within your `.ipynb`
environment (Jupyter Notebook, JupyterLab, Google Colab).

## Installation

```bash
pip install NexusViewPro
```
